
itg.py is an inversion transduction grammar as descriped here:
http://acl.ldc.upenn.edu/J/J97/J97-3002.pdf

Requires 3 files:
probs
    alignment probabilities for input language words to output language words
    need not be complete
    format: inputword putputword prob

sentences.in
sentences.out
    translated sentences in the input and output languages
    must be aligned line for line

running ./itg.py will output the most probable alignments for the words in the given sentences.
